    <h2>1. Introduction</h2>\
    <p>Koda ("we," "our," or "us") operates the Skalap mobile application ("App"). This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and protect your information when you use our App.</p>\
    <p>We are committed to protecting your privacy and complying with Swiss data protection laws, GDPR (for EU users), and other applicable regulations.</p>\
\
