        <li>We do NOT store credit card numbers</li>\
        <li>We receive only transaction confirmations</li>\
    </ul>\
\
    <h3>2.2. Information Automatically Collected</h3>\
    <p><strong>Usage Data:</strong></p>\
    <ul>\
        <li>Videos analyzed (URLs and metadata)</li>\
        <li>Analysis results and history</li>\
        <li>Features used within the App</li>\
        <li>Time and date of activities</li>\
    </ul>\
