        <li><strong>Payment Processing:</strong> Stripe, Apple (payment transactions)</li>\
        <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> Google Analytics (anonymized usage data)</li>\
        <li><strong>Customer Support:</strong> Email service providers</li>\
